en disant "ahoy" ?

248
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:50,741
Ahoy.

249
00:15:53,416 --> 00:15:54,417
J'aime bien.

250
00:15:55,959 --> 00:15:56,766
Amy ?

251
00:15:56,891 --> 00:15:57,941
C'est toi ?

252
00:15:59,027 --> 00:16:00,083
Tu as bu ?

253
00:16:01,491 --> 00:16:03,590
Tu veux parier
sur mes jolies petites quoi ?

254
00:16:05,214 --> 00:16:07,508
Très bien.
On arrive.

255
00:16:08,684 --> 00:16:09,696
Qu'y a-t-il ?

256
00:16:09,821 --> 00:16:11,821
